## Build

```bash
cmake --preset relwithdebinfo                         # CPU-only dev build
cmake --build build/relwithdebinfo --parallel
ctest --test-dir build/relwithdebinfo --output-on-failure

cmake --preset release-cuda                           # CUDA + Python
cmake --build build/release-cuda --parallel
export PYTHONPATH="build/release-cuda/bindings/python:scripts/python"
python scripts/python/demo_linalg.py
```

---

## Hardware

- **CPU**: Ryzen 7 9800X3D — AVX-512, 96 MB 3D V-Cache. Use `simd_traits<double>::width = 8`. Tile sizes larger than textbook due to huge L3.
- **GPU**: RTX 3060 12 GB, Ampere SM 8.6. 28 SMs. Default launch: 256 threads/block.
- **OS**: Arch Linux, GCC 16 / Clang 22, Python 3.12+.
